{{Infobox Union|<!-- Please include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. --> |name= CST |country= [[Venezuela]] |affiliation= |members= |full_name= Workers' Socialist Centre of Venezuela |native_name= Central Socialista de Trabajadores y Trabajadoras de Venezuela |image= |founded= 2008 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Caracas]], Venezuela |people= |website= |footnotes= }}
The '''Workers' Socialist Centre''' ({{lang-es|Central Socialista de Trabajadores y Trabajadoras de Venezuela}}, CST) is a federation of [[trade union|labor unions]] in [[Venezuela]] that was founded in August 2008, representing 1,280,000 affiliated workers.<ref>[http://alainet.org/active/25606&lang=es]</ref> It explicitly aims to support a transition to socialism in Venezuela.<ref>[http://www.aporrea.org/trabajadores/a59697.html]</ref>
